body:
We updated dependencies ([chokidar](https://www.npmjs.com/package/chokidar)) around v0.12.1, can you help to figure out whether this problem is related to `chokidar` or not?

``` javascript
var chokidar = require('chokidar');
var watcher = chokidar.watch('current directory', {
  ignored: /[\/\\]\.|node_modules/, 
  persistent: true,
  ignoreInitial : true
}).on('all', function(event, path) {
  console.log(event, path);
});
```

Appreciate!
